[h2]Compatibility Information[/h2]
[list]
[*]probably NOT compatible with mods that modify FE Awakening events or the War in Heaven.
[*]possibly compatible with mods modifying un-awakened Fallen Empires.
[*]probably compatible with mods modifying the AI, fleet compositions, ship layouts and/or economy of Fallen/Awakened Empires.
[*]compatible with ZoFE
[/list]
If there are any compatibility issues you are especially interested in, leave a comment.

[h2]Installation & Uninstallation[/h2]
This mod should only be (un)installed for games where NO end-game crisis or Fallen Empire awakening events have been triggered.

